  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataPlugin
    Interface implemented by Data Plugins in order to fetch data from an external source and import it into the framework.

    Interface implemented by a Data Visualisation plugin.

    ClientPoint

    DataPoint

    Main
    Instantiates a new GUI.
    ParameterList
    A list of parameters created by Visualisation Plugins for the framework to display as sliders.

    Library class for visualisation plugins that implements custom data structures to enhance querying for data that is "nearby" other Geo-Tagged data.
